Ranger Help for: diversion
==========================

SYNTAX:      diversion <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     35
SKILL TYPE:  attack

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to create a combat distraction, confusing
and disorienting the target. A successful diversion debuffs the target,
reducing their combat effectiveness for a short duration. This can
include penalties to hit chance, dodge, and awareness. The distraction
draws on the Ranger's cunning and knowledge of the surrounding terrain
to exploit the environment.
